Package events.elevatorEvents

Class Summary
CreateElevator This class is used to simulate the event if an elevator needs to be created.
ElevatorAI This class is used to simulate the AI which drives the elevators, it updates the People waiting on the floors for elevators.
ElevatorGettingFixed This class is used to simulate the event when an elevator is getting fixed.
ElevatorMoves This class is to simulate the event where an elevator moves It makes an elevator move either up or down.
ElevatorStopsWorking This class is used to simulate the event where the elevator stops working for the duration specified.
PeopleEnteringElevator This class is used to simulate the event where people enter the elevator.
PeopleLeavingElevator This class is used to simulate the event where people leave the elevator
